# SCHERBELBERG

*/ˈʃɛʁbɛlbɛʁk/ ([German, toponym, male: "mountain of shards" in Leipzig](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Category:Rosentalh%C3%BCgel_(Leipzig)))*

